### 8. 旅行社电子行程单【多条件筛选列表】（必传 agencyId）
GET http://localhost:8080/agency/order/list?agencyId=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8‑1. 筛选【待确定】状态的行程单
GET http://localhost:8080/agency/order/list?agencyId=1&orderStatus=待确定
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8‑2. 筛选【青城山】团队名的行程单（模糊）
GET http://localhost:8080/agency/order/list?agencyId=1&teamName=青城山
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8‑3. 组合筛选：待出发 + 团队名含成都
GET http://localhost:8080/agency/order/list?agencyId=1&orderStatus=待出发&teamName=成都
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 新增旅行社电子行程单（新接口）
POST http://localhost:8080/agency/order/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "agencyId": 1,
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "driverId": 1,
  "guideId": null,
  "teamName": "青城山一日游",
  "peopleCount": 22,
  "startAddress": "重庆",
  "endAddress": "青城山景区",
  "startTime": "2026-04-20T08:30:00",
  "orderStatus": "待确定"
}

