#====================== 2. 告警信息接口测试 ======================
### 2.1 查询所有告警信息
GET http://localhost:8080/alert/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 查询单个告警详情（id=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/alert/get/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.3 系统自动检测并生成告警
GET http://localhost:8080/alert/autoCheck
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.4 值班员审核告警通过（id=1，操作员：值班员张三）
POST http://localhost:8080/alert/checkPass
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

id=1&operator=值班员张三

### 2.5 领导审批并发布告警（id=1，领导：李四）
POST http://localhost:8080/alert/publish
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

id=1&leader=李四

### 2.6 直接处置告警（id=1，处置结果：已处理，处置人：王五）
POST http://localhost:8080/alert/handle
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

id=1&handleResult=已联系景区处理完毕&handler=王五

### 2.7 查询告警处置记录（alertId=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/alert/handleList/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ====================== 3. 投诉管理接口测试 ======================
### 3.1 提交投诉
POST http://localhost:8080/complaint/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "visitorName": "游客张三",
  "visitorPhone": "13800138000",
  "level": "一般",
  "content": "导游服务态度差，未按约定讲解景点",
  "guideId": 1,
  "agencyId": 1,
  "status": "待处理"
}

### 3.2 处理投诉（id=1，处理人：管理员，处理结果：已道歉，状态：已办结）
PUT http://localhost:8080/complaint/handle/1
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

handleUser=管理员&handleResult=已联系游客道歉并补偿，游客满意&status=已办结

### 3.3 查询所有投诉列表
GET http://localhost:8080/complaint/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.4 按状态查询投诉（待处理）
GET http://localhost:8080/complaint/list?status=待处理
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.5 按旅行社ID查询投诉（agencyId=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/complaint/list?agencyId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.6 按导游ID查询投诉（guideId=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/complaint/list?guideId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.7 查询单个投诉详情（id=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/complaint/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.8 删除投诉（id=1）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/complaint/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}